{"tid":2353931,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Oh My Girl 祉呼詮釋復古畫報　分享開設 SNS 的心境與 2021 願望","createTime":"2021-01-05T06:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T08:30:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a03666c2d162b3d4dc8b143cd30e66998a1b93f","tid":2353931,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_37137f1fbae5c90550aefb104521d528/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-05/132785-891893.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_37137f1fbae5c90550aefb104521d528%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-05%2F132785-891893.png&h=616c191f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長相古典的 Oh My Girl 成員祉呼最近拍攝了一系列復古畫報，同時深入分享不為人知的細膩心思，也透露 Oh My Girl 想在今年開唱的熱切盼望！<br />\n<br />\n時尚雜誌《THE STAR》最近公開了和祉呼攜手拍攝的畫報，以「重返 1920 年代的時空旅行」為主題，以簡單而典雅的復古服飾搭配華麗首飾，呈現出祉呼獨特的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_72e8dba0bf8243dca8d5257fdde21bf9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-05/132785-891894.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_72e8dba0bf8243dca8d5257fdde21bf9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-05%2F132785-891894.png&h=1bea1cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6eca61974589828282494a8ce8644997/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-05/132785-891895.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6eca61974589828282494a8ce8644997%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-05%2F132785-891895.png&h=8ef62e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n談起最近引發話題的防疫全套裝備，祉呼透露：「我覺得防疫一定要從自己先徹底做起，因為我也可能影響到隊友、工作人員還有他們的家人。」她貼心地說：「我覺得比起自己感染，我更怕自己對別人造成傷害，所以一直很小心。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3ad581a2553e1363245bf51ce3d0dc36/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-05/132785-891896.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3ad581a2553e1363245bf51ce3d0dc36%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-05%2F132785-891896.jpg&h=3bddec7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_208225b3c0aaf1f4c1b25c7ca8b5d1a5/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-05/132785-891897.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_208225b3c0aaf1f4c1b25c7ca8b5d1a5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-05%2F132785-891897.jpg&h=d9860b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為 Oh My Girl 七人中最晚開 Instagram 的成員，祉呼也解釋了原因：「我之前一直很猶豫要不要開 Instagram。因為粉絲一直在等我、希望我開帳號，所以我就開了。我應該跟粉絲溝通，我覺得我不能擋住這條（溝通的）管道，加上沒辦法常常見到粉絲，所以就更深刻地覺得應該開個帳號。」<br />\n<br />\n「希望 2021 年能在有延伸舞台的地方開演唱會。」祉呼透露：「這是 Oh My Girl 的夢想，希望今年一定要開專場演唱會！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a8312d9f74a181ef8f7dd9eef01b6da1/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-05/132785-891898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a8312d9f74a181ef8f7dd9eef01b6da1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-05%2F132785-891898.jpg&h=6366a5fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"799659127fded71ee5e9fc6886e9ee8bde22b891","tid":2353931,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"幾靚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7168271ffea260e5d5b638b1183183dd6a64928","tid":2353931,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"唔錯...幾有味道"},{"pid":"fc0d3fe8302b1494ed46e7ad585ee6d866ceba19","tid":2353931,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"799659127fded71ee5e9fc6886e9ee8bde22b891","tid":2353931,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"幾靚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:10:12.000Z","msg":"normal la...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42805d36808b4a113681f2c2c